52
00:03:04,580 --> 00:03:05,570
Hong Sang-Tae!

53
00:03:07,620 --> 00:03:09,520
Au, to bolí! Kruci.

54
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:16,950
Hong Sang-Tae! Hong Sang-Tae!

55
00:03:26,620 --> 00:03:27,870
Jídlo! Jídlo je tu!

56
00:03:27,870 --> 00:03:30,180
